AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 1827* House Bill No. 2038
by inserting the following as a new subsection (d) immediately following subsection (c) in
SECTION 2:
(d) A department, agency, or other unit of state government shall not accept or
make payment in gold or silver coin unless authorized by statute or a joint resolution of
the general assembly.
